The paper discusses the challenges and proposed solutions for resource allocation and scheduling in millimetre wave backhauls, which are relevant to the fields of networking (cs.NI), information theory (cs.IT), multimedia (cs.MM), computer security and cryptography (cs.CR), and computer communication (cs.COM). However, since the focus is primarily on networking and communication, cs.NI is the most likely category, followed by cs.IT and cs.MM.
